Title: randomString
Description: Generates a string of the specified length filled with random bytes (including zero bytes). Not all characters may be printable.
length — String length in bytes. Positive integer.
String filled with random bytes. String.
Examples: SELECT randomString(30) AS str, length(str) AS len FROM numbers(2) FORMAT Vertical;
EffectiveSQLsRefined: SELECT randomString(30) AS str, length(str) AS len FROM numbers(2) FORMAT Vertical;
